panels.description: Disclaimer: if the time window is too big, the value reported as complete will be **incorrect**.

targets.rawSql:
WITH summary AS (
    SELECT recorded_at as "time",
           measure,
           tag,
           value,
           ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY measure
                                 ORDER BY recorded_at DESC) AS rk
      FROM visor_processing_stats p)
select time,
       max(value) filter (where measure = 'completed_count')::numeric /
       max(value) filter (where measure = 'count') as "value"
from summary
where $__timeFilter(time)
  and tag = $tag
group by time
order by time;
